title: Beats By Dre Presents Stampd: New York Fashion Week Debut
description:
When music influences fashion.

Chris Stamp of Stampd shares his inspiration for his latest collection for his New York Fashion Week debut.

asset.author: Beats by Dre

transcripts: Going into the show at New York’s men fashion week, it’s our best collection today. Its label the new soldier and I’m really excited to show it. We’re putting pieces out there to address the new generation. Some people call it avant chic, some people call it contemporary, but I know it’s just something different. The music was a huge element one of my best friends Brian I had him produce the track for us and the first time we heard it it just really tied everything together. I’m nervous for sure people are always gonna look down on something they’re not used to. They don’t understand how much blood, sweat, and tears has been put into the collection. We've worked day and night to get to this point this is it welcome to the future.
